We were having this issue in even without using the error mailer (just when trying to render the error page at all) and I'm sure it was due to the same issue.  Adding this custom middleware solved the issue:

```python
## Dev only
class StopRunserverPlusShutdownMiddleware(object):
    def process_request(self, request):
        try:
            del request.META['werkzeug.server.shutdown']
        except KeyError:
            pass
```

